# SSL Certificate Directory
# Place your SSL certificates here:
# - taxeen.crt (SSL certificate)
# - taxeen.key (Private key)
# - taxeen.chain.crt (Certificate chain, if applicable)
#
# For Let's Encrypt, use certbot to generate certificates:
# certbot certonly --webroot -w /var/www/certbot -d taxeen.com -d www.taxeen.com
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit actual SSL certificates to version control!
# Add *.crt and *.key to .gitignore
